== Overview ==
The Cobalt Hydron reactor offers extra recharge over the [[Hydron Core Mk. II|Core Mk. II]].

== Where to Acquire ==
The Cobalt Hydron Reactor can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.

